'''克里斯多福·艾萨克·「比兹」·斯通'''（{{lang-en|'''Christopher Isaac "Biz" Stone'''}}，{{bd|1974年|3月10日}}）<ref name="noemail">{{cite web|url=http://www.bizstone.com/2000/04/no-emails-today-except-couple-work.html|title=Biz Stone:No Emails Today|author=Biz Stone|accessdate=2010-02-14|date=2000-04-12|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100213184210/http://www.bizstone.com/2000/04/no-emails-today-except-couple-work.html|archivedate=2010-02-13}}</ref>，美国创意总监，软件工程师和商人，[[Twitter|Twitter]]的创建者之一，现为[[Twitter|Twitter]]的创意总监。

==生平==
他参与创建的项目包括[[Xanga|Xanga]]、[[Blogger|Blogger]]、[[Odeo|Odeo]]以及[http://obvious.com/ Obvious] {{Wayback|url=http://obvious.com/ |date=20210321095706 }}。另外他还出版了两本有关博客的著作：《Blogging: Genius Strategies for Instant Web Content》(New Riders，2002年) 和《Who Let The Blogs Out?》 (St Martins，2004年)。<ref>{{cite web|author=Stone, Biz|title=About bizstone|url=http://flickr.com/people/biz/|work=Flickr|publisher=Yahoo!|accessdate=2010-02-14|archive-date=2019-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190504060430/https://www.flickr.com/people/biz/|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[杰克·多西|杰克·多西]]和比兹·斯通大约花两周时间写出了Twitter的原型。<ref name=Glaser>{{cite news|author=Glaser, Mark|title=Twitter Founders Thrive on Micro-Blogging Constraints|url=http://www.pbs.org/mediashift/2007/05/twitter-founders-thrive-on-micro-blogging-constraints137.html|date=May 17, 2007|publisher=Public Broadcasting Service (PBS)|accessdate=2010年2月14日|archive-date=2013年4月24日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130424161815/http://www.pbs.org/mediashift/2007/05/twitter-founders-thrive-on-micro-blogging-constraints137.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 比兹·斯通现居[[加利福尼亚|加利福尼亚]][[伯克利|伯克利]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.diablomag.com/Diablo-Magazine/July-2009/Best-of-the-East-Bay-Stars-amp-Standouts/#2 |title=The Tweet Life - Biz Stone - Best of the East Bay - Diablo Magazine - July 2009 |access-date=2010-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100218014333/http://www.diablomag.com/Diablo-Magazine/July-2009/Best-of-the-East-Bay-Stars-amp-Standouts/#2 |archive-date=2010-02-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 他毕业于[[韦尔斯利_(马萨诸塞州)|马萨诸塞州]]{{tsl|en|Wellesley High School|韦尔斯利高中}}。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.boston.com/bostonglobe/magazine/galleries/2009/1220/BOTYpoll?pg=8 |title=Who should be the 2009 Bostonian of the Year? |access-date=2010-02-14 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170144/http://www.boston.com/bostonglobe/magazine/galleries/2009/1220/BOTYpoll?pg=8 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

